6+8+10+\cdots+(6+2n-2)=6n+(0+2+4+\cdots+2n-2)=\\6n+2(0+1+2+\cdots+n-1)=6n+2\frac{(n-1)n}{2}=6n+(n-1)n=n^2+5n
4n+110
n^2+5n=4n+110
n^2+n-110=(n+11)(n-10)=0
n=10
\begin{align} 4n + 110 & = \dfrac n2\left(6 + 6 + 2(n-1)\right) \\ \\ & = \dfrac n2(12) + \dfrac {2n\cdot (n-1)}{2}\\ \\ & = 6n + n(n - 1) \\ \\ & = 6n + n^2 - n \\ \\ 4n + 110 & = n^2 + 5n\end{align}
\begin{align} n^2 + 5n - 4n - 110 & = 0 \\ \\ n^2 + n - 110 & = 0\\ \\(n-10)(n+11) &= 0\end{align}
n = 10, \; n=-11
n > 0
n = 10
